profile:
Green Side Up Contracting Inc. is a professional member of Landscape Ontario & we are an authorized TrexPro - Platinum status!

Over the last 22 years, we have established ourselves within the construction industry as an honest and reputable contractor.  We have earned this reputation by shaping the company around four core values: honesty, transparency, quality of workmanship, backed by above industry-standard warranties!

As the President of Green Side Up Contracting Inc. and a board member of the Toronto Chapter of Landscape Ontario, PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT and delivering EXCELLENCE are two of Jay's key priorities.

         ****************************10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY - FENCING ****************************

Green Side Up Contracting Inc is a consistent award-winning, construction company that focuses on delivering high-quality workmanship and superior customer service.  We put our trust into our clients with extremely favorable payment terms - pay when the job is completed! We are active members of our community and believe in helping those who are less fortunate.

Services provided include but are not limited to:

-> Fence Construction (80' linear feet minumum)
 
-> Interlocking & Landscape Construction

-> Deck Construction (200 sq foot minumim) 

    - Trex
    - Cedar

***

Not only does Green Side Up Contracting Inc focus on PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT by offering a TEN-YEAR structural WARRANTY on fencing, we also believe that doing business together should be simple and transparent.

***

Please use our SELF SERVE CALCULATORS to obtain an INSTANT ESTIMATE for your DECK, FENCE or INTERLOCK project:

FENCE CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/fence-building-calculator/

DECK CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/deck-calculator/

INTERLOCKING CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/interlock-cost-calculator/

***

Please be sure to check our work by visiting:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/greensideupcontracting/

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRNuc7PofUOEHCwMf7NdUzQ/videos?view_as=subscriber

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GreenSideUpContracting/

We would also invite you to come on site during the construction process, so you can see our work in progress!

***

Building is fun, business is great, people are terrific and life is wonderful! 

I ask that you put your trust into Green Side Up Contracting - we not disappoint!!

On your side,

Jay Saveall

www.greensideupcontracting.com

profile:
We are Action Home Services, and we always take action for every construction service that you need. Based in Toronto, Ontario, we are a general contracting company that specializes in a wide range of services. We will help you to design and build an outside living area of your dream. Do not wait! Take action with Action Home Services. Check our website at http://actionhomeservices.ca/ to find out more. 

Our Mission
We aim to become one of the most successful construction companies within Toronto, Ontario. This mission will not happen if our services are not up to the level of what our customers are expecting. Thus our main aim is to provide the best services to our customers. Our level of professionalism will become our barometer for customer satisfaction. We also aim to make it a point to have strong ties with our customers so we can grow the level of our professionalism and gain more trust among our clients.

Our Vision
Our dream is to become the one-stop shop for any kind of construction service that any of our clients need. We initially started with interlocking and asphalt paving, but we are now venturing into other services such as landscaping, pressure washing and sealing, concreting, decks and fences, demolition services and many more. We already have a wide range of service offerings, but we are not satisfied with just these. We are excited about every project that we perform and our possibilities for improvement and additional services are endless.

Our Commitment 
We commit to do whatever it takes to achieve the level of satisfaction our customer deserves. Our workmanship will leave a lasting mark and one that will be a reminder of our professionalism and close ties with our clients. We gained the trust of our customers through hard work that pays off when we see our clients happy with the outcome of our services. We will strive to be cooperative and readily available for any queries or requests our customer needs.

Canada’s Gardenland is a leading domestic landscape construction and maintenance service provider in the Greater Toronto area. Our team of lawn specialists utilizes their knowledge of lawn science and their skills of artistic application to create the perfect look for your specific landscaping scenario. We understand that each property and client taste is different so we work diligently with you and your surroundings to tailor the best approach for meeting those needs. Canada’s Gardenland has both the tools and the experience available to help you bring your landscaping dream to life.
Canada’s Gardenland designs, creates, maintains and provides tools for domestic landscaping projects in the Greater Toronto area. Both artistic landscaping skills and applied lawn science is utilized in order to achieve the perfect atmosphere and our professional team works closely with clients to ensure that projects meet specific needs and requirements.

Proper landscaping requires the application of various aspects in order to make your property look its best. Therefore, Canada’s Gardenland first helps with the design and creation of the right landscaping techniques that complement the natural lay of land as well as any man-made structures on the premises. We also offer a variety of interlocking stone techniques that provide landscaping accents through beautifully designed and applied walkways, driveways and patios.

We can also apply creative outdoor lighting effects so that your landscape is transformed into a stunning sight of beauty after dark and provides safety to those visiting after hours. Quality landscaping maintenance is also offered through sod fertilization, trimming, grooming, replanting and cleaning so that your property always looks its best.

profile:
Singular Focus:

Most landscape and renovation companies try to serve many types of customers at the same time; homeowners, shopping centers, office buildings, golf courses, and the list goes on. They are pulled in all directions trying to be everything to everyone. At Captain Handy Co, we focus on one customer, you, the homeowner. We have a singular focus on bringing you the best landscaping and interior renovation, the best customer service, and the best value for your home. When you consider that quality renovation can improve the value of your home by 10%-15%, why wouldn’t you hire the one company that focuses specifically on residential landscaping? We are Your Residential Landscape and interior renovation Company.
Easy:

Our business makes your life easier. We are committed to improving the quality of life for our customers so they can spend their time on other things. Our customers are busy and have hectic lives. They do not have time to deal with different companies for lawn care, mowing, design, patio building. Captain Handy Co. offers turn-key solutions to your landscape needs. One call connects you with one of our very qualified Landscape Advisors who will make sure that you are delighted with your landscape. It is that easy.
Hassle-Free:

Ever notice how some companies make it a hassle just to do business with them? Who needs hassles? Life is complicated enough as it is. With Captain Handy Co, you can expect fast response times, clear and concise proposals, and work to be done how and when we promise it would be. You can also expect us to stand behind our work, show up when we say we will and take care of the little things that can take a landscape,renovation and experience, from blah to wow! We take away the hassles so all you have to do is enjoy your landscape.
Professional:

With 5 years under our belts, we know a thing or two about being the professional contractor of choice. Our staff has an average tenure rate of over twelve years, and some team members have been with us for over two decades! They undergo extensive and on-going training to not only assure that your renovation looks fantastic, but also to make sure that you are treated superbly. Our staff members are clearly recognizable in their sharp uniforms so you will know who is on your property. With so many companies claiming to be “professional”, isn’t it nice to work with a company that actually is?
Our Values:

At Captain Handy Co, we provide Tender Loving Care to both you and your interior and landscape renovation. These are our Values:
•	Treat people honestly, fairly and with respect in all situations
•	Create a comfortable environment in which to work and do business
•	Be open to problems and complaints, and work quickly to a fair resolution
•	Present a professional image and working safely
•	Have a “can-do” attitude
•	Stand behind our commitment to quality and service
•	Be active, responsible and positive citizens in the communities in which we work

profile:
Mr. Interlock Landscape & Construction is a professional residential and commercial design and build firm servicing the York Region and Greater Toronto Area communities.
 
With over 30 years of experience in interlocking and paving installations, we help our clients create a distinctive design element that will magnify their homes allure, increase its value while offering a unique look customized to meet their landscape desires.
 
We take pride in providing our clients with original and timeless designs, innovative ideas, quality construction, prompt and professional service, outstanding warranty and seamless flow of project implementation from start to finish.
 
Our construction expertise spans across a variety of materials from natural stone, flagstone, marble to cobblestones, standard pavers, concrete and asphalt.
 
We also specialize in a variety of project types such as driveways, patios, stairs, retaining walls, swimming pools, outdoor kitchenettes, outdoor living spaces, outdoor lighting, outdoor audio and more.
 
Our mission is to enhance and beautify the communities we enter by supplying our clients with a uniquely designed landscape project that adheres to our motto "Do It Once, Do It Right". All while providing our clients with unparalleled service through our consultation, planning and execution resulting in long lasting relationships and an abundance of word of mouth referrals.

profile:
Winner of many awards including a national and provincial award for best residential design. With passion and creativity and over twenty years' experience in beautifying properties all over the GTA, Land-Con prides itself on customer satisfaction and customer experience before, during and after the project is completed. We are very honest with our customers, keeping them up to date regularly with the progress of the project. We strive to give our customers the highest quality of work, starting with our very experienced in house, award winning landscape designers, as well as extremely professional and respectable trade personal on the job site, with the owners them selves over seeing every single project on a daily basis.
We have received industry wide recognition for design and build, professionalism and customer satisfaction.


ACCOMPLISHED TEAM
Active Member of Landscape Ontario and Bild.  ICPI and NCMA certified.  Techno-Bloc Pro installer.  Permacon Pro installer.  2016 Winner of 2 Landscape Awards of Excellence, 2017 winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence, 2019 National Award, 2020 Winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence and the Van Casey award for best Design. 
At Land-Con, our principles, passion and reputation speak for themselves.  Our valued clients will agree; excellence in project management, coupled with our highly qualified management and crew are second to none.


COMPASSIONATE CARE
We build to capture and reflect the unique vision our clients trust us to create while abiding to strict standards and timelines.  We value your expectations and opinion and respect the importance of budget guidelines.  The job site will always be left cleaned up and tidy and ready for next day construction.  We respect your property and will be courteous and considerate of you and your neighbors.


AFTER CARE
At Land-con we believe that after a project is completed the aftercare with our customers is just as important as any part of the project.  If at any time after the project is completed, you have any questions or concerns we are here to help.  We back our workmanship with a five year extended warranty.  This warranty is transferable if you happen to sell your home within the five year period.  Our top priority is customer service.  We take pride in providing courteous prompt responses to all clients past and current.

ABOUT THE OWNERS

Growing up together for the past 30 years, Ofer Winkler and Jeremy Lerner have formed a strong friendship which naturally became a great partnership.  They have both been in the landscape industry since 1997 giving each of them over 20 years experience in this industry.  Each one brings to the table their specialized onsite experience, and combined with their in class courses that they have attended over the years, makes them a team like no other.  Ofer and Jeremy have a passion for the landscape industry and each project they built over the years, which gives each home owner their own unique experience.  Their mission and vision is to give every home owner and project they build the attention and time they deserve.  This has made Land-Con a well-respected company by home owners, suppliers and even competitors around the GTA.  Together, they are an award winning team that transforms their clients' vision into reality, while providing professional services that meet the budget and time line.

profile:
Since we started serving the GTA in 2006 we have been dedicated to providing the ultimate finished product. We specialize in residential and commercial landscaping including Re/Re work such as trench and boulevard restoration. All of our work is designed to not only be aesthetically pleasing but also withstand the harsh Canadian climate. We also provide a complete property maintenance service for condo complexes, plazas, and residential. The end goal is to provide the best quality service to our clients. 

All jobs are fully insured and bonded. 

**

We provide helpful suggestions and create beautiful custom designs suitable for any budget. The sales representative's job isn't over after the contract is signed, they are there to help throughout the process, ready to answer any questions you might have and handle changes at the customers request in a professional and timely manner. Daily updates on how the project is going are provided to ensure that everything has been completed to our customers needs. We warranty all of our work. Our plan is to make sure that all of our customers enjoy working with us and enjoy their new outdoor space. 

**

Please contact us and we would be happy to send a sales representative out for a free quote with no obligation.

profile:
Outdoor Lighting Perspectives is the world's largest full-service outdoor lighting company, and we are proud to have our fixtures enjoyed at more than 150,000+ homes across North America. 

Whatever your outdoor lighting needs, we have the experience and expertise to get it done right the first time.

WHAT WE DO:

We want to transform your outdoor living spaces in the best way possible. Some of our exquisite outdoor lighting options include:

-Accent lighting to subtly show off your property’s best features
-Architectural lighting to highlight your home’s unique beauty
-Pool lighting to keep your nightly swims safe
-Patio and deck lights to add excitement to your nighttime entertaining
-Garden lighting to accentuate your stunning landscaping
-Path lighting to guide your guests where they need to go
-Up-lighting for home facade, trees, and outdoor artwork

From a single small garden that needs just a touch of light, to a sprawling estate home that needs lighting with zone control automation, we offer it all.

Call us today for a free at-home consultation, and one of our lighting designers will make a customs lighting design for your unique property.

WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT:

We are dedicated outdoor lighting designers and installers. We do one thing, and we do it the best. We aren't a sprinkler company or lawn care company moonlighting in outdoor lights when times are slow. We will be here to take the call when your lights need maintenance years down the road.

We manufacture our lights by hand, mostly in the United States but some right here in Toronto, so we can control the entire chain of quality from raw materials to your beautiful garden. 

Our designers, installers, and service crews are all our own staff: we do not use sub-contractors. With Outdoor Lighting Perspectives, your satisfaction is guaranteed in writing and backed by our 30 year on-site warranty.

THE TRUSTWORTHY CHOICE:

How can you find an outdoor lighting contractor you can trust to get the work done right, on time, and safely? 

We have been independently vetted by a third-party for our complete and up-to-date liability insurance and workers compensation coverage, our safety and training compliance, and our long established track record of happy customer referrals and testimonials. 

Companies claiming to do lighting come and go, but we're celebrating 20 years and our warranty is backed by our international network of 60+ locations. We'll install your lights today, but we'll also maintain them for years to come.

THE NEXT STEP:

We offer free design consultations and free quotes. Please contact us to discuss your outdoor lighting needs and how we can be of assistance.

Category: Landscape Contractors and Designers.

Modern Landscape Design. Toronto's premier modern landscaping company. 

Your modern lifestyle, outdoors. Creating usable, functional and refined environments with a modern aesthetic. 

Green Apple offers a complete residential landscape design and build service in GTA Toronto, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Vaughan, Woodbridge, Kleinburg, Nobleton, Caledon, Richmond Hill, and Thornhill. With over 30 years of landscaping experience and a portfolio of award-winning gardens, we are dedicated and passionate about creating the perfect garden for our clients.

We are now pleased to offer three dimensional (3D) plans as part of our design process. This is in addition to our standard two dimensional (2D) plans. The 3D plans provide you with the opportunity to visualize your landscape makeover in photorealistic 3D pictures of your designed landscape and actually see what your landscaping will look like before it is built! See our 3D designs on Homestars and Houzz.

profile: In 2007, Green FX Landscaping was founded by Pino and Rob Arpa and began services the following spring. Since then, Green FX Landscaping has continued to provide exceptional, complete lawn maintenance for residential and commercial properties.  The knowledgeable technicians at Green FX Landscaping are made up of passionate people, each having years of experience in lawn and garden maintenance, new lawn installation (hydro seeding, terraseeding and sodding), and landscape management.  Building long-lasting and trusting relationships with our customers is very important to us and we strive to provide our clients with exceptional customer service and satisfaction. We take the time to get to know each of our clients so that we can better understand their vision and goals for their project to provide stunning results!  At Green FX Landscaping, your landscape is not only a representation of you but it is also a reflection of us; so you can take comfort in the fact that pride, precision, and hard work goes into every project.  Whether your property needs are residential or commercial, we will work with you to create the perfect lawn treatment plan that compliments your style and budget while protecting your investment and preserving the environment.

profile:
Bestloc Interlocking is trusted and respected landscape design and Installation company operating in the Greater Toronto and Surrounding Areas. As a proud and certified member of ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), we provide our clients with award winning landscape designs and industry leading installations. Bestloc was found on two main principles of encouraging family outdoor living and building structures that last.

Many years ago, Ryan Morant, founder and president started out being a labourer, where he developed his passion for the trade. He then became a foreman, and inspector, and subsequently a teacher. Under his leadership, our professional team of highly skilled and qualified personnel provides innovative landscape designs. With over 15 years of planting and masonry experience, and hundreds of thousands of square feet laid, Bestloc Interlocking embodies the values of strength, performance, and passion. We are dedicated to providing our clients with custom landscaping solutions.

We are in constant communication with our friends at ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), and are always up-to-date on industry leading techniques on landscape designs and installations. We offer good communication with our clients from the beginning of each project to its completion. Our experienced project management means your project is completed on time and on budget.

Furthermore, we complete every task with a commitment to integrity and a devotion to excellence using the best quality products guaranteed to leave a lasting impression. If you wish to create the finest outdoor living experience for you and your family, please do not hesitate to contact Bestloc Interlocking for a free consultation/estimate.

profile:
We started our Landscape and Interlocking Stone business in 1994 based on three pillars:  Integrity, Quality, and Service.

ONE job at a time… Unlike many other businesses we do ONE job at a time. It is important to us to be able to focus all our efforts into each customer so that they get the best in personal attention and their project is completed as expected and on time.

No Sub-Contracted Work…   We do all the work ourselves. Our employees are highly qualified, talented, and honest. We wouldn’t trust your project and our reputation to anyone else.

We deliver what we promise to do. We carry out our work according to what our customers want and expect. We strive to deliver the best results at the least possible cost for the client.
Our work exceeds construction standards and client’s expectations. We take satisfaction in showing our customers how their project is been done so that they may appreciate the workmanship that goes into their project.

As a Landscape Contractor and Designer....
Our Goal… To exceed the expectations of every client by doing our work with Honesty, Quality, and Professionalism.                                  
Our approach… We first listen to what our clients want and make suggestions based on that and our experience. We then proceed to work in an efficient and flexible manner through every phase of the project to suit the client's needs.
 
We are happy to provide you with the following services and more:
Patios, walkways, steps, porches, verandas, pergolas, driveways, flower beds, gardens, planting, sprinklers, lighting, stone BBQs, stone fireplaces, and much more.

Letter from Danilo Otero, owner of Royal Town Landscape Development, March 2012:

Dear Customers,

I would like to thank you and congratulate you for helping children in Nicaragua go to school. Because of you, we were able to provide school supplies to 100 kids this past month and we are already working to provide another one hundred sets of school supplies this Summer. 

Thank You!  You made a big difference.

Regards,

Danilo

profile: At AquaSpa Pools we believe that a pool and its surrounding landscape is more than just a home improvement. It is an exciting new lifestyle. Quality pool and landsacping design increases the value and beauty of your property, brings tranquility and enjoyment to your backyard and is an expression of who you are. As every person and family is different, so is every project. Your backyard retreat will be customized to suit your individual needs and bring your dream surroundings to life. From inviting pools and spas, to flagstone paths and rejuvenating gardens, we treat every project as if it were our own home. DESIGN Our certified pool and landscape designers will listen to your ideas and wishes, and offer their experienced input. Then they will visualize your dream space, using the latest CAD design programs and hand-drawn renderings. QUALITY AquaSpa Pools & Landscape Design uses only the best construction materials, combined with experienced quality workmanship. Our knowledge of proper construction techniques will give you years of trouble-free enjoyment. TIMELINES We constantly amaze our clients with the speed in which we complete our projects. We go to great lengths to ensure that projects stay on schedule and that the final results surpass all expectations. WARRANTY We partner with the best equipment suppliers in the industry to provide our clients with premium products and comprehensive manufacturer warranties. AquaSpa Pools & Landscape Design stands by all of the work that we do, making the enjoyment of your new backyard retreat worry-free. SERVICE At AquaSpa we not only design and build your pool and landscaping, we also provide reliable after-service. Our familiarity with your unique project and our trained staff's knowledge of the equipment used will ensure efficient service and maintenance. After-services include pool opening and closing, safety cover installations, liner replacement and more. ENVIRONMENTAL RESPONSIBILITY Our pools use intelligent multispeed pumps and 2" plumbing to reduce electrical consumption, increase efficiency and pass savings along to you,. Cartridge style filters are used to avoid wasting water during backwashes, not to mention conforming to City by-law reference sewer use. Using safe water systems eliminates the need for harsh chemicals and the pollution associated with the production, packaging and transportation of these dangerous materials. Option R value insulation is used behind the steel panels and in the plumbing trenches to reduce the loss of heat. SPECIALIZING IN Pools, Spas, Hot Tubs, Water Features, Infinity Edge, Landscaping, Patios, Cabanas, Gazebos, Outdoor Kitchens & Fireplaces OUR PROFESSIONAL SERVICES INCLUDE: Renovations/Upgrades, Salt Water Conversions, Liner Replacement/Repair, Opening/Closings, General Repairs, Inspections, Safety Cover Installation ACCESSORIES Automatic Pool Cleaners, Pool Covers, Automatic Pool Covers, Fitness Swim Jets, Outdoor Lighting, Pool Controls, Water Accents, Salt Systems, Solar Systems

profile:
Filedmasters Synthetic Grass is second to none in the synthetic turf industry. Since 1991 we have provided the Canadian market with high-quality artificial turf products that are ideal for putting or golf greens, playgrounds, landscaping and more. 

Due to increasing water shortages and environmental concerns regarding chemicals and lawn fertilizers, more homeowners, business owners, and city governments are opting to install our products. Our synthetic grass eliminates the need for constant maintenance such as irrigation, mowing, fertilizing, aerating and more.

Fieldmasters products are durable, versatile, safe, economical and 100% recyclable. Most importantly, they look and feel so much like real natural sod that they enhance the look of any residential or commercial landscape. We are proud to offer our clients a high-quality product that will stand the test of time.

We also offer ull landscape and design for residential, recreational and commercial properties.

Residential: Grass replacement (back yard, front yard, balconies, roof tops), pool deck covering, interlocking patios, retaining walls, fencing, path ways and flag stones. 

Recreational: Sports fields such as soccer, football, lacrosse and lawn bowling.

Commercial: Day cares, community centers,  dog kennels, dog spas, gold centers, fitness centers.

....and many more!

- We are proudly Canadian
- We are located in GTA, in turn can provide quick response as required
- Proven success various of installation (installers are certified)
- Our product is North American made from one of the largest artificial turf manufacturer in the world. They are leaders in manufacturing artificial turf for various uses, industries and geographic locations
- We’ve been in business for 25+ years.
- Our turf is technologically advanced synthetic turf system that is engineered for durability, performance, and appearance
- Our backing is a premium design/quality, resulting in better drainage, better suited for pet management and weed prevention
- Our product is 100% made from new materials, no part of the turf is recycled or has been used previously
- Our product is 100% recyclable, heaven forbid you wanted to remove it
- Our product is 100% lead free and fire tested (have certifications to prove it)
- Our product doesn’t attract insects, animals won’t eat it, weed will not grow through it,  it’s allergen-free, and accidents wash right through
- Our product is designed to deter against various elements: high human and non-human traffic, heavy rain, heavy snow, high winds, high sun
- 10 year limited warranty
- Fully insured and WSIB
- Many references (see the pictures for a small sample of what we have accomplished)

Thanks for landing here! Let us tell you a little bit about our crew and how we came to be. 
RTA Landscape and pools started as a side hobby 30+ years ago. The owner, Rei, worked for the largest construction company in Canada since he was 17 and fell in love with the industry immediately. He worked for other large family run companies and dabbled in different areas of construction. REI TANAKA
Owner & Operator
- 30+ Years Experience

- 3D Structure Studios Expert

profile:
VP Landscape is more than just a company, it is years built on hard work, dedication and passion for the industry. In his younger years, owner, Vito lived in Sala Consilina in the province of Salerno, in Italy. In a town where agriculture and farming was a main source of income, Vito was always intrigued by landscaping. When he immigrated to Canada he began his journey in landscape where he worked alongside his brothers. VP Landscape was born when Vito decided it was time to chase his dreams and begin his very own landscaping company.

Today, you will see VP Landscape and their work in high-end, residential properties in and around the GTA. Vito, alongside his son, Michael work together to envision and then execute the unique designs that they imagine for each individual client. They pride themselves on their ability to respect client privacy during and upon completion of every project. Their speciality remains in formal and manicured properties in which their expertise and passion evidently shine through.

Many of the details that you see in their work have been inspired by gardens and landscapes all over the world. Their various style adaptability, outstanding attention to detail and family orientated nature makes them one of the most reputable and personable landscape companies in Canada.

profile:
Welcome to Simply Exquisite, we are a construction and renovations general contractor in Toronto, serving the GTA and surrounding areas.

For over 20 years we have worked with property and homeowners providing them with high caliber commercial and home renovation services. We have earned our reputation as one of the best general contractors in the GTA through our trade expertise and professionalism. We are customer-service driven, pay extra attention to details, and deliver a quality product, on time and budget.

We approach every project with this simply promise: Every home renovation, general contracting, and construction project will be Simply Exquisite. That is our guarantee.

Whether you are looking to do a home renovation in Toronto, from kitchen design and renovations, to bathroom remodels and basement finishing, or something smaller like having your kitchen refaced or installing basement heated flooring, you can trust the best construction company in Toronto to give you the peace of mind of a job well done.

We offer award-winning renovation services that come with a 5-year warranty. We provide in-house design services and counseling, free of charge, with a licensed architectural designer. We extend this added value with every one of our projects so that you can be sure that your project will satisfy your needs.

profile:
Affordable Landscaping Services in Tottenham
A pristine lawn or a tastefully designed outdoor space adds immeasurable value to a house or any other property. It enhances the aesthetics of the place while also improving the experience of those who reside in it or visit it. At Green Machine Landscaping & Maintenance, we truly understand the importance of improving and maintaining the outdoors of your property. We are a passionate team of professionals who render superior landscaping services in Tottenham and other parts of Ontario. We do everything to beautify your property, from laying interlocks and masonry to yard work, while combining nature’s grandeur with our skillfully crafted designs. Our work is informed by an in-depth understanding of horticulture, landscaping and aesthetics. Working with different types of materials, styles and designs, we are able to achieve the exact results you are looking for.

We're social here:
https://www.instagram.com/green_machinelandscaping/

profile:
Greenfield Landscaping and Lawn Care is a fully insured company and has over 30 years of professional experience building, maintaining, and managing lawn care and exterior projects. The company has been in business since 1997 and is owned and operated by Mansoor Reihani. Mansoor not only has the knowledge and understanding of agricultural sciences, but he has the natural creativity to design and implement any beautiful exterior you can think of!

Mansoor Reihani has a Masters degree (M.Sc.) specializing in Agriculture from Arizona State University from the United States and has the knowledge to help you identify which types of conditions are perfect for your flowers, trees, bushes, natural stones, interlock, etc. He also currently manages an outstanding team of trained landscapers to ensure quality and beautiful work for every single customer.

profile:
THE TOTAL PHILOSOPHY
OUR DEDICATION
The relationship with the customer is the aspect that we enjoy maintaining the most. We believe in being loyal to the people who are loyal to us. We offer a variety of promotions and discounts to our existing and future customers. 

We want to develop a relationship that is productive, respectful, and long lasting and we are willing to do the little things to make it work

Connect with TOTAL through Facebook, Twitter, e-mail, or even do it the old fashion way and give us a call! We are always happy to talk with you and discuss any property maintenance needs you may have.

CONNECT WITH US
Total Property Services
WHO WE ARE
At TOTAL Property Services we have a strategy that aims to add both convenience and value to our customers.

We are a one stop shop for ALL of your property maintenance needs. Take a look at our list of Residential services and Commercial services, you will be impressed.

All properties are different and unique maintenance needs may exist at your property. Simply contact TOTAL, and we will find a way to get the job done!

How it works: When you contact us for a quote on lawn care, or anything else for that matter, we do an assessment of your property. Upon establishing a relationship, we provide you with a full list of all the services that we provide related to your property and of course the price.

That’s it! No pressure, no annoying hassling of any kind, just keep TOTAL in mind and if you decide you need some help around the house, give us a call or an email and we will be happy to help out.

We're social here:
https://www.facebook.com/Total-Property-Services-274251702750608/
https://www.instagram.com/total.property.services/

Call Us: 647-273-9111
services:
Stop wasting your leisure time on lawn care and landscape maintenance. Seasonal changes make caring for your property a frustrating inconvenience. In the spring, fertilizing treatments are required to give you the lush green turf to enjoy through the warm months. During the summer season, when many of us look forward to enjoying vacation time, grass grows quickly and weeds need to be kept at bay. In the autumn, our yards can get blanketed with leaves and other debris that have to be cleared away for winter, just in time for us to trade the rake for a shovel to dig out our driveways.

profile: We are a dedicated, creative landscape design and build team servicing the Toronto, Richmond Hill, York Region and West Durham regions. At Humber Valley Landscaping, we want to create beautiful, functional outdoor spaces that fit your lifestyle. We know that each project requires specific expertise, a keen creative eye and quality products and materials. Our team will take a professional and personable approach toward creating your own outdoor oasis. We specialize in design, full project installations, planting of trees, shrubs and plants, installation of armor stone retaining walls, excavation and grading, and drainage issues.  We have been in business since 2001 and look forward to working with you on your project.
services:
DESIGN BUILD SERVICE

Install a new front, back or full landscape project for your property. If you are looking at a new patio, walkway, retaining wall or gardens, we will work within your budget to develop your space.


DESIGN BUILD SERVICE

Install a new front, back or full landscape project for your property. If you are looking at a new patio, walkway, retaining wall or gardens, we will work within your budget to develop your space.

PLANT INSTALLATION

Let our professionals design a new planting theme for you.

ARMOUR STONE

Install some of our gorgeous armour stone as accents in your new garden or let us build you a beautiful retaining wall.

PATIOS, WALKWAYS, DRIVEWAYS

We work with high quality materials to build you a long lasting walkway, stunning patio or the clean look of an interlock driveway.

RETAINING WALLS, RAISED GARDEN

Add interest to your property with raised gardens and professionally installed retaining walls.

FLAGSTONE

we can take any area of your property and build a relaxed random flagstone sitting area. We also specialize in square cut flagstone that is mortared to concrete surfaces such as porches and landings.

LANDSCAPE LIGHTING AND ARCHITECTS

The right landscape lighting will give your property ambiance at night. You won’t want to go inside!

IRRIGATION

Professionally installed high quality systems designed for your property. No more hoses and sprinklers wasting precious water. At Humber Valley Landscaping we have two Certified Irrigation Technicians on staff.

profile:
ROYAL SCAPES

Landscape and construction services

WHAT WE DO
We are your go to company for any landscape and construction needs. From bricklaying, fences, garden beds, property maintenance, snow removal to building sheds. We do it all! We are your one stop do it all company!

WHO WE ARE
We are a family run business that want to make a difference in what people call home. Our quality and expectations are beyond average and we thrive to keep that alive. We want customers to feel like royalty, and have the highest confidence in the outcome of their yard when we are done.  

We're social here:
https://www.instagram.com/royal.scapes2021/
https://www.facebook.com/RoyalScapes2021/
services:
LAWN CARE

We cut grass, rip up and re lay sod, grass seeding and we make burnt patches in the grass come alive.


WOOD WORK

Do you need somewhere to store your tools but don't have any place to put them? Will build your sheds! Do you have a nice back yard but nowhere to sit? Will build your decks! Do you have pets and no privacy? Will build your fence!


STONEWORK

We do everything from laying brick to working with concrete. We build pads, walkways, fire places, driveways, retaining walls, walls, and even garden borders. 


MAINTENANCE

Do you have a beautiful big yard but struggle to keep it clean all the time? Call us and we will have it looking good as new.  We will keep your grass clean and your garden beds cleaner. 


GARDENING

Do you love the look of flowers but can't find the time to plant them? We will do it for you. Maybe you don't have a garden but you want one, we will design it and make it happen for you!
warranty_terms: Yes. 3 Years on Workmanship. Kindly ask for more details.

profile:
Dimitriadis Design Build is a cheerful, creative company dedicated to providing unique landscape design and high quality landscape, renovation and new build construction. We offer superior craftsmanship in the construction of exterior projects (garden design, structures) and interior projects (renovations, additions). What makes us extraordinary is our forethought in custom designed elements – not only can we imagine it, but we can build it! 
Customer service is extremely important to us. We strive to have our clients find their experience with Dimitriadis Design Build mind blowing with original designs, innovative solutions and smooth running project management.
